<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.1">
<l>orunā yakamā yōṭa vulakuṭa ṉāṇṭavar</l>
<l>karunāy kavarnta kālar citaikiya pāṉaiyar</l>
<l>perunāṭu kāṇa vimmaiyi lēpiccai tāṅkoḷvar</l>
<l>tirunā raṇaṉṟāḷ kālam peṟaccintit tuymmiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who ruled the worlds together, there being one leadership, so that [their enemies?] ran,</l>
<l>their legs seized by black dogs, with pots that are broken(?)</l>
<l>will take alms in this very birth, while the great land looks on.</l>
<l>Be saved by contemplating, so as to reach in time, the feet of sacred Nārāyaṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
